        <item>
            <title>2.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 21:12:37 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>44</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- Session titles now evolve with the conversation — AI-generated titles refresh periodically as the discussion progresses, not just on the first message
- Title generation works for all providers (Anthropic, DeepSeek, custom API) with automatic fallback when AI generation is slow

### Changes
- Titles use a concise, fact-based style instead of roleplay-influenced summaries
- Debug builds now use Apple Development signing identity

### Fixes
- Resumed sessions no longer have their titles permanently frozen — they can now update as the conversation continues
]]></description>
